snippet.title: Nomori - Pre-Alpha Update Trailer - Play Now
snippet.description:
The Nomori Pre-Alpha Update is Live! 

We recently transitioned from Tech Demo to Pre-Alpha and want to give players a first-hand experience with our mind-bending game. 

Enjoy 18 new puzzles and a complete overhaul of the games visuals, sound and gameplay.

Play it here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2092190/Nomori_Prologue

Wishlist the full game: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2932680/Nomori/ 

------------

Join our discord: https://discord.gg/mAKStQrY52
